# Chemist SOP

  [bold]1.[/bold] The Chemist is [bold]not[/bold] permitted to experiment with explosive mixtures;

  [bold]2.[/bold] The Chemist is [bold]not[/bold] permitted to experiment with poisonous mixtures and/or narcotics;

  [bold]3.[/bold] The Chemist is [bold]not[/bold] permitted to experiment with Life or other highly experimental Omnizine-derived mixtures;

  [bold]4.[/bold] The Chemist is [bold]not[/bold] permitted to produce alcoholic beverages;

  [bold]5.[/bold] Chemists in conjuction with [color=#5b97bc]Medical Doctors[/color] and must make sure that Cloning is stocked with Biomass if set up;

  [bold]6.[/bold] The Chemist must ensure that the Medbay is stocked with at least enough medication to handle Brute, Burn, Respiratory, and Toxin damage. Failure to follow this Guideline or attempting to follow this Guideline within thirty (30) minutes is to be considered a breach of Standard Operating Procedure;

  [bold]7.[/bold] The Chemist is [bold]not[/bold] allowed to leave Chemistry unattended if the Medbay is devoid of Medication, except in such a case that Chemistry is unusable.
